---
{/* BREAKDANCE: hand-authored from structure.json */}
import site from '@/lib/site';
---

<section class="section section--tint s3-why">
  <div class="container">

    <h2 class="s3-why__heading">Why Microneedling Works When Other Treatments Haven't</h2>

    <div class="s3-why__cards">

      <div class="s3-why__card">
        <h3 class="s3-why__card-title">Precision Technology</h3>
        <p class="s3-why__card-body">The SkinPen creates micro-channels at precise depths to target your specific skin concerns, from acne scars to fine lines.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="s3-why__card">
        <h3 class="s3-why__card-title">Natural Healing Response</h3>
        <p class="s3-why__card-body">By triggering the skin's natural healing response, microneedling stimulates collagen and elastin production for results that improve over time.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="s3-why__card">
        <h3 class="s3-why__card-title">Universal Compatibility</h3>
        <p class="s3-why__card-body">Unlike laser treatments, microneedling is safe for all skin types and tones with no risk of hyperpigmentation.</p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="s3-why__cta">
      <a
        href={site.calcomUrl}
        class="btn btn--primary btn--lg"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
      >
        Schedule Now
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .s3-why__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-lg);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .s3-why__cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-md);
    width: 100%;
  }

  .s3-why__card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    padding: var(--space-md);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    background: var(--color-bg);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.05);
  }

  .s3-why__card-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h3);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .s3-why__card-body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .s3-why__cta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .s3-why__cards {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .s3-why__cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .s3-why__cta .btn {
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>
